the-butterflies-remember-him-japanese-students-discovery-uncovers-astonishing-insect-memory/articleshow/132304921.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-10T18:09:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132306283,imgsize-77482.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Billionaire Larry Ellison once fought the entire city of San Jose so he could land his private jet at midnight, but when it came to buying a $490 million megayacht, he did it over lattes and two emails]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132311763.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Larry Ellison, the tech titan, exemplifies contrasts through extravagant purchases and turbulent legal encounters. His lavish superyacht was created with little legal fuss, showcasing a whimsical side. Yet, after five years, he embraced minimalism amidst a notable drop in his wealth due to stock market changes. As Oracle’s fiscal health is now scrutinized, all eyes are on its future direction.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/billionaire-larry-ellison-once-fought-the-entire-city-of-san-jose-so-he-could-land-his-private-jet-at-midnight-but-when-it-came-to-buying-a-490-million-megayacht-he-did-it-over-lattes-and-two-emails/articleshow/132311763.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/billionaire-larry-ellison-once-fought-the-entire-city-of-san-jose-so-he-could-land-his-private-jet-at-midnight-but-when-it-came-to-buying-a-490-million-megayacht-he-did-it-over-lattes-and-two-emails/articleshow/132311763.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-10T18:38:49+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132312648,imgsize-133126.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[H-1B visa revoked: Man says he deeply regrets not paying $600 traffic fine by deadline]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132312459.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[An unpaid traffic ticket caused the revocation of an individual's H-1B visa, showcasing the potential consequences of administrative oversights. The man in question said he moved to a new apartment and missed the payment notice.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/h-1b-visa-revoked-man-says-he-deeply-regrets-not-paying-600-traffic-fine-by-deadline/articleshow/132312459.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/h-1b-visa-revoked-man-says-he-deeply-regrets-not-paying-600-traffic-fine-by-deadline/articleshow/132312459.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-10T18:16:42+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132312506,imgsize-124846.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Truce and fire: The ghost of Versailles haunts Trump. But is Iran overplaying its hand?]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132311423.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[President Trump declared the June 17 ceasefire with Iran over, ordering fresh US strikes. Iran responded by targeting tankers in the Strait of Hormuz, escalating tensions. The conflict's tempo is now largely controlled by Iran's ability to disrupt oil shipments. Both sides face pressures, with neither in a decisive position to end the war. Managed instability with periodic attacks and negotiations is the likely immediate outcome.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/truce-and-fire-the-ghost-of-versailles-haunts-tru